<subSubSection id="CCFD0CC3FFF8014463A5F2C9912388A2" pageId="26" pageNumber="49" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="84585F48FFF8014463A5F2C9912388A2" blockId="26.[151,760,713,896]" pageId="26" pageNumber="49">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFF8014463A5F2C9926989C2" bold="true" box="[151,280,713,736]" pageId="26" pageNumber="49">Comments.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="E07622B9FFF80144622EF2C992E989C2" author="REID C. A. M." box="[284,408,713,736]" firstAuthor="REID" journalOrPublisher="Australian Journal of Entomology" pageId="26" pageNumber="49" pagination="1 - 9" part="38" refId="ref33192" refString="REID C. A. M. 1999: Reappraisal of the genus Taumacera Thunberg with descriptions of two new species from South-East Asia (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae: Galerucinae). Australian Journal of Entomology 38: 1 - 9." title="Reappraisal of the genus Taumacera Thunberg with descriptions of two new species from South-East Asia (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae: Galerucinae)" type="journal article" year="1999">REID (1999)</bibRefCitation>
transferred this species to 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFF80144619AF2C993B78822" authorityName="Thunberg" authorityYear="1814" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Taumacera" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="49" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFF80144619AF2C993B78822" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="49">Taumacera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
without any comments. The 
<typeStatus id="5B5CE1EAFFF8014462C9F2E991298822" box="[507,600,745,768]" pageId="26" pageNumber="49">holotype</typeStatus>
is deposited in the ZMUH and I studied it many years ago. Based on my notes and photographs taken at that time, I am excluding this species from 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFF801446267F34992BD8842" authorityName="Thunberg" authorityYear="1814" box="[341,460,841,864]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Taumacera" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="49" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFF801446267F34992BD8842" box="[341,460,841,864]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="49">Taumacera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and I provisionaly classify it as 
<taxonomicName id="43E724CBFFF8014463FBF36992CC88A2" authorityName="Bezděk" authorityYear="2019" baseAuthorityName="Laboissiere" baseAuthorityYear="1936" box="[201,445,873,896]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Hyphaenia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="49" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tonkinensis">
<emphasis id="B693835AFFF8014463FBF36992CC88A2" box="[201,445,873,896]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="49">Hyphaenia tonkinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(comb. nov.).
</paragraph>
